Balletts and madrigals to fiue voyces with one to 6. voyces: newly published by Thomas Weelkes. Weelkes, Thomas, 1575 (ca.)-1623.
[142] p. : music
Printed by Thomas Este, the assigne of William Barley, In London : 1608.
Five partbooks. At head of title, part 1: "Cantus."; part 2: "Altus."; part 3: "Tenor."; part 4: "Quintus."; part 5: "Bassus.". Signatures: [A]² B-D⁴; [A]² B-D⁴; [A]² B-D⁴; [A]² B-D⁴ E¹; [A]² B-D⁴. At least the Folger Shakespeare Library and the Library of Congress have the sextus leaf (E1) bound with the quintus partbook. Reproduction of the original in the Library of Congress.
